      "content": "i know that sounds high but i've seen some wellness influencers saying that \"loading doses\" are actually the best way to fix a massive deficiency quickly. they say standard doses are too slow to make a difference when you're already feeling depleted. if i only do it for like 10-14 days, isn't that basically just a quick reset for my system? wouldn't the body just process it out?",
